note right of Student
  Primary Actor
  Target Age: 10-18 years
  Main user of the platform
end note

note right of System
  Secondary Actor
  Handles automated processes:
  - Token verification
  - Progress tracking
  - Points calculation
  - Badge unlocking
end note

note bottom of UC1
  Validates age (10-18)
  Collects: username, age,
  birthday, password, email
  (optional), gender (optional)
end note

note bottom of UC13
  Awards 50 points
  Triggers celebration
  Updates progress
end note

note bottom of UC25
  Points Sources:
  - Module: 50 points
  - Quiz question: 10 points
  - Perfect quiz: +20 bonus
  - Badge: 10-100 points
end note

note bottom of UC26
  Level Progression:
  L1: 0-199 (Beginner)
  L2: 200-499 (Explorer)
  L3: 500-999 (Learner)
